  "subject": "Fix vulnerabilities in sdc-be-common",
  "commit_message": "Fix vulnerabilities in sdc-be-common\n\n- update gson (2.8.7 -> 2.8.9)\n- update apache httpclient (4.5.13 -> 4.5.14)\n- update owasp esapi (2.4.0.0 -> 2.5.5.0)\n- update portal epsdk-logger (2.5.0 -> 3.4.0)\n- update json-simple (1.1 -> 1.1.1)\n- bump snapshot version to 1.11.1-SNAPSHOT\n\nIssue-ID: SDC-4747\nChange-Id: Id1e79f4ef28794cb7823b88ec3cdc8575bd849cb\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <Fiete.Ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
